messages.subject: Re: [AlwaysLearning] good ol' Marion
messages.msgSnippet: If you really want a giggle, watch good ol Marion trying to play a Mongol warlord in The Conqueror.  He s laughable.  Like a cowboy dressed up for Halloween
messages.messageBody:
If you really want a giggle, watch good ol' Marion trying to play a
Mongol warlord in The Conqueror. He's laughable. Like a cowboy dressed
up for Halloween in a funny dress.

OK, it's a generational thing. I've always LOATHED John Wayne.

Betsy

**In a message dated 11/19/2002 6:41:58 PM Eastern Standard Time,
SandraDodd@... writes:
> I used to love reminding people my
> parents' age that John Wayne was NEVER a cowboy, and NEVER a soldier, he
> was
> an actor who wore makeup. They'd just about burst into tears.)

I can't quit laughing!

Still giggling.

Probably all night! **
